WEBVTT

00:00.801 --> 00:03.671
[ DRAMATIC MUSIC PLAYS ]

00:31.599 --> 00:33.101
[ GUNSHOTS ]

00:33.101 --> 00:35.103
[ TIRES SCREECH ]

00:35.103 --> 00:36.770
Terry:
YOU SONS OF BITCHES!

00:36.770 --> 00:39.773
EVERY ONE OF YOU DESERVES
WHAT'S COMING!

00:39.773 --> 00:41.041
[ GUNSHOTS ]

00:41.041 --> 00:43.010
I'M GONNA KILL
EVERY LAST ONE OF YOU!

00:43.010 --> 00:45.346
[ GUNSHOTS ]
[ WOMAN SCREAMING ]

00:45.346 --> 00:49.150
THERE'S A COMMON SAYING
AMONG L.A.P.D. OFFICERS.

00:49.150 --> 00:52.220
"LEAVE THE JOB IN THE LOCKER
WITH YOUR UNIFORM."

00:52.220 --> 00:54.322
IT'S EASIER SAID THAN DONE.

00:54.322 --> 00:57.658
WE GET THIS 415.

00:57.658 --> 01:02.363
A YOUNG GIRL, 10 MAYBE...
CLAIMING CHILD ABUSE.

01:02.363 --> 01:04.365
WE ROLL UP. SHE'S CRYING.

01:04.365 --> 01:05.966
SHE GOT THIS HAIRCUT
LIKE SINГ©AD O'CONNOR.

01:05.966 --> 01:10.638
IT'S ALL...MESSED UP
AND CHOPPY.

01:10.638 --> 01:12.506
ANYWAY, HER PARENTS DID IT
WHEN SHE WAS ASLEEP,

01:12.506 --> 01:13.874
AND SHE WANTS THEM
ARRESTED.

01:13.874 --> 01:15.276
[ CHUCKLES ]
RIGHT?

01:15.276 --> 01:16.610
SO, THEY COME OUT,
AND THEY SAY THEY DID IT

01:16.610 --> 01:18.312
BECAUSE THEY DIDN'T WANT HER
TO BE SO VAIN.

01:18.312 --> 01:21.982
IF THEY UGLY HER UP,
SHE'LL BE MORE INTERESTING

01:21.982 --> 01:25.519
AND THAT BEING AN OUTCAST
BUILDS CHARACTER.

01:25.519 --> 01:27.688
BEACHWOOD CANYON?
SILVER LAKE.

01:27.688 --> 01:30.224
AH. CLOSE ENOUGH.
[ LAUGHS ]

01:30.224 --> 01:33.394
GOD. [ SIGHS ]
IDIOTS.

01:33.394 --> 01:35.663
WHAT DID YOU DO?

01:35.663 --> 01:38.065
I TOLD THEM
THEY HAD TO GET RID

01:38.065 --> 01:40.434
OF WHATEVER
CHILD-REARING BULLSHIT

01:40.434 --> 01:42.136
THAT THEY WERE READING...
[ LAUGHS ]

01:42.136 --> 01:44.004
...AND USE
SOME COMMON GODDAMN SENSE.

01:44.004 --> 01:46.374
OH. I MISS IT.

01:46.374 --> 01:47.908
I...
[ CHUCKLES ]

01:47.908 --> 01:51.412
MORONS MOST OF ALL.
HMM.

01:51.412 --> 01:53.414
[ SIGHS ]
ANOTHER ONE?

01:53.414 --> 01:55.583
NO. I, UH --
I GOT TO GET HOME.

01:55.583 --> 01:56.884
AW, COME ON, YOU PUSSY.
[ LAUGHS ]

01:56.884 --> 01:59.019
ONE MORE. COME ON.
NO, I WISH I COULD.

01:59.019 --> 02:01.355
ALL RIGHT, ALL RIGHT.
[ SIGHS ]

02:01.355 --> 02:04.057
HEY, UH...DO YOU WANT TO CATCH
THE LAKER GAME ON SUNDAY?

02:04.057 --> 02:06.059
I GOT TWO TICKETS.

02:06.059 --> 02:07.928
I...
MIGHT HAVE SOMETHING.

02:07.928 --> 02:09.763
UM, LET ME CHECK.
I'LL GET BACK TO YOU.

02:09.763 --> 02:12.132
ALL RIGHT. OR WE COULD
JUST GRAB A BEER, YOU KNOW?

02:12.132 --> 02:14.134
ALL RIGHT.
I'LL GET BACK TO YOU.

02:14.134 --> 02:15.669
ALL RIGHT.

02:24.212 --> 02:25.379
OOH-WHEE.
THAT WAS GOOD.

02:25.379 --> 02:26.914
IS THAT
WHAT I THINK IT IS?

02:26.914 --> 02:28.249
THINK IT'S A GUN?

02:28.249 --> 02:31.118
WHY WOULD YOU BRING THAT...
TO DINNER?

02:31.118 --> 02:32.453
WELL,
WHAT IF SOMEBODY COMES IN

02:32.453 --> 02:33.787
AND STARTS SHOOTING UP
THE PLACE?

02:33.787 --> 02:35.489
I'VE NEVER BEEN
IN A RESTAURANT

02:35.489 --> 02:36.824
WHERE SOMEONE'S
SHOT UP THE PLACE.

02:36.824 --> 02:39.360
IT HAPPENS ALL THE TIME.
THANK YOU.

02:39.360 --> 02:41.362
AND IF IT HAPPENED
AND I WASN'T PREPARED,

02:41.362 --> 02:42.830
I'D NEVER FORGIVE MYSELF.

02:42.830 --> 02:44.632
MY HERO.
THANK YOU.

02:44.632 --> 02:46.300
THOUGH THEY SAY
YOU'RE NOT SUPPOSED TO

02:46.300 --> 02:47.568
BRING YOUR WORK
HOME WITH YOU.

02:47.568 --> 02:49.002
PLEASE,
LIKE YOU'RE ONE TO TALK.

02:49.002 --> 02:50.904
I'VE SEEN YOU AT THE KITCHEN
TABLE GRADING PAPERS,

02:50.904 --> 02:52.306
MAKING THOSE, UH --
THOSE LITTLE --

02:52.306 --> 02:53.441
WHAT DO YOU CALL
THOSE LITTLE THINGS?

02:53.441 --> 02:54.808
CANDY DREIDELS.
CANDY DREIDELS.

02:54.808 --> 02:56.510
I'VE SEEN YOU MAKING THOSE
CANDY DREIDELS.

02:56.510 --> 02:58.612
[ SIGHS ] I-I JUST -- I'D REALLY
HATE TO BE IN A SITUATION

02:58.612 --> 03:00.648
WHERE I NEEDED A CANDY DREIDEL
AND I DIDN'T HAVE ONE.

03:00.648 --> 03:03.183
ALL RIGHT. OKAY. YOU MADE
YOUR POINT, ALL RIGHT?

03:03.183 --> 03:05.185
[ LAUGHS ]
SHERMAN.

03:05.185 --> 03:07.821
DREW! HEY!
WHAT'S UP, MAN?

03:07.821 --> 03:09.022
HOW YOU DOING? UH...

03:09.022 --> 03:11.259
UH, THIS IS MY, UH --
MY GIRLFRIEND, BROOKE.

03:11.259 --> 03:12.660
UH, THIS IS DREW.
HELLO.

03:12.660 --> 03:14.362
WE USED TO KNOW EACH OTHER
BACK IN THE DAY.

03:14.362 --> 03:15.596
HOW YOU BEEN, MAN?

03:15.596 --> 03:17.064
GOOD. GOOD.
UM...WHAT YOU BEEN UP TO?

03:17.064 --> 03:20.067
YOU KNOW, THIS AND THAT.
I SEE, UH, BUSINESS IS GOOD?

03:20.067 --> 03:22.603
YEAH, YOU KNOW, WITH ALL
THE DISPENSARIES POPPING UP,

03:22.603 --> 03:25.172
I HAD TO, UH, DIVERSIFY A BIT,
BUT I'M COOL.

03:25.172 --> 03:26.740
CHECK IT OUT.

03:26.740 --> 03:28.742
IF YOU NEED ANYTHING, UH,
JUST GIVE ME A CALL, ALL RIGHT?

03:28.742 --> 03:31.612
YEAH. YEAH, YOU GOT IT.
ALL RIGHT. SEE YOU LATER.

03:31.612 --> 03:34.114
YEAH,
TAKE CARE OF YOURSELF.

03:34.114 --> 03:36.317
THAT DUDE USED TO SELL
ME AND MY FRIENDS WEED

03:36.317 --> 03:37.451
IN HIGH SCHOOL.

03:37.451 --> 03:40.321
REALLY?
YEAH. YEAH, I GOT THAT.

03:40.321 --> 03:45.593
SO..."GIRLFRIEND"?

03:45.593 --> 03:47.595
Sammy: NO.
Justine: COME ON, SAMMY!

03:47.595 --> 03:49.263
CAN'T BE AROUND ANY OF THAT.
JUST DO YOUR THING.

03:49.263 --> 03:51.332
PLAY WITH US,
MR. BODYGUARD.
I'LL WAIT OUT HERE.

03:51.332 --> 03:53.000
NO, NO, NO.
STAY!

03:53.000 --> 03:54.902
LET ME KNOW
WHEN YOU'RE DONE.
PLEASE, MR. BODYGUARD?

03:54.902 --> 03:57.237
VERY CUTE.

03:57.237 --> 03:58.406
[ SIGHS ]

03:58.406 --> 04:00.608
[ CAMERA SHUTTER CLICKS ]

04:06.146 --> 04:08.015
[ SIGHS ]

04:12.720 --> 04:14.722
[ GUNSHOTS ]

04:18.892 --> 04:21.762
WAIT HERE!

04:25.566 --> 04:27.100
[ GUNSHOTS ]
[ TIRES SCREECH ]

04:27.100 --> 04:28.602
Terry:
YOU SONS OF BITCHES!

04:28.602 --> 04:30.904
EVERY ONE OF YOU DESERVES
WHAT'S COMING!

04:30.904 --> 04:32.440
[ ALARM BLARING ]

04:32.440 --> 04:33.974
YOU WANT SOME OF THIS?!
[ GUNSHOTS ]

04:33.974 --> 04:36.444
[ TIRES SCREECH ]

04:36.444 --> 04:38.679
I WILL DELIVER YOU!

04:38.679 --> 04:40.047
TRY IT!
[ GUNSHOTS ]

04:40.047 --> 04:42.616
I'LL GUN YOU DOWN!

04:43.784 --> 04:47.455
[ GUNSHOTS ]

04:47.455 --> 04:48.656
[ SCREAMING ]
STOP IT! SHUT UP!

04:48.656 --> 04:50.524
LET GO OF ME!
SHUT UP!

04:50.524 --> 04:52.059
SHUT YOUR MOUTH!

04:52.059 --> 04:53.260
[ GRUNTING ]

04:53.260 --> 04:54.595
[ SCREAMING ]

04:54.595 --> 04:57.398
YOU WANT SOME OF THIS?!

04:59.733 --> 05:02.403
[ SCREAMING ]

05:02.403 --> 05:04.505
[ GRUNTING ]

05:04.505 --> 05:06.206
[ CAMERA SHUTTERS CLICKING ]

05:06.206 --> 05:08.342
AAH! [ GRUNTS ]

05:08.342 --> 05:09.677
[ SIREN WAILING ]

05:09.677 --> 05:11.345
GET THE FUCK OUT OF HERE!

05:11.345 --> 05:13.681
I AM SO SORRY.

05:13.681 --> 05:16.384
I FINALLY FIND A BABYSITTER
I LIKE, AND SHE GETS STREP.

05:16.384 --> 05:18.552
AH, IT HAPPENS.
[ SIGHS ]

05:18.552 --> 05:19.720
YOU GETTING OUT OF TOWN,
HUH?

05:19.720 --> 05:21.722
YEAH,
I'M FLYING TO ARIZONA TONIGHT.

05:21.722 --> 05:25.092
I'LL BE BACK IN THE MORNING.
HAVE AN EXECUTION TO GO TO.

05:25.092 --> 05:26.093
OH, BOY.

05:26.093 --> 05:27.595
IT'S A LONG STORY.

05:27.595 --> 05:29.930
ONE THAT YOU'RE GONNA SHARE
WITH ME, I'M SURE.

05:29.930 --> 05:32.800
OH, YEAH, OF COURSE,
BUT THANK YOU GUYS SO MUCH

05:32.800 --> 05:34.502
FOR TAKING CARE
OF CHRISTOPHER FOR ME.

05:34.502 --> 05:35.969
OH, PLEASE.
YOU'RE DOING ME A FAVOR.

05:35.969 --> 05:38.672
EVERY 18 MONTHS, ANGELA TALKS
ABOUT HAVING ANOTHER KID.

05:38.672 --> 05:41.775
NO BETTER BIRTH CONTROL THAN
HAVING A SCREAMING BABY AROUND.

05:41.775 --> 05:44.812
WHAT'S UP, BUDDY?
I'M TALKING ABOUT YOU.

05:44.812 --> 05:47.781
BRYANT.

05:47.781 --> 05:51.485
[ INHALES DEEPLY ]
OH, SORRY.

05:51.485 --> 05:54.021
YOU SHOULD TAKE THE DAY,
GET SOME REST.

05:54.021 --> 05:55.523
I'M FINE.
SAMMY.

05:55.523 --> 05:58.058
OH, NO.
I-I NEED MY DAYS FOR NATE.

05:58.058 --> 06:00.060
I'M GOOD.

06:04.297 --> 06:06.166
[ VELCRO RIPS ]

06:06.166 --> 06:07.668
Reyes: OH, THERE HE IS!

06:07.668 --> 06:09.670
WHOO! HEY, HEY!
[ CHEERS AND APPLAUSE ]

06:09.670 --> 06:12.673
HOLD ON, HOLD ON, HOLD ON.

06:12.673 --> 06:16.176
OH, ALL RIGHT,
"L.A.P.D. OFFICER SAMMY BRYANT

06:16.176 --> 06:19.379
"RUSHED INTO HARM'S WAY,
TACKLING THE GUNMAN

06:19.379 --> 06:21.048
"AND PROTECTING THE POP SINGER

06:21.048 --> 06:23.116
FROM THE WOULD-BE ASSASSIN'S
BULLET."

06:23.116 --> 06:24.251
[ LAUGHTER ]

06:24.251 --> 06:25.586
SHE WAS THREE BLOCKS AWAY,
OKAY?

06:25.586 --> 06:27.220
IT HAD NOTHING TO DO
WITH HER.

06:27.220 --> 06:29.923
UH-HUH. THIS ONE SAYS
YOU'RE BANGING HER, THOUGH.

06:29.923 --> 06:32.926
OH, YEAH,
I'M BANGING NIA, RIGHT?

06:32.926 --> 06:34.995
I NEVER EVEN MET HER
TILL LAST NIGHT.

06:34.995 --> 06:36.897
OKAY, VERY FUNNY.

06:36.897 --> 06:38.265
[ LAUGHTER ]
VERY, VERY GOOD.

06:38.265 --> 06:40.501
GO AHEAD.
OH, YEAH.

06:40.501 --> 06:42.069
[ CHEERS AND APPLAUSE ]

06:42.069 --> 06:44.438
HEY, WE GOT MORE
WHERE THAT CAME FROM, BRYANT.

06:44.438 --> 06:46.106
YO, SHERMAN.
YOU BETTER WATCH OUT, MAN.

06:46.106 --> 06:47.875
THEY GONNA WANT TO THROW HIM
ON THAT POSTER.

06:47.875 --> 06:51.645
Watters: ALL RIGHT. ALL RIGHT.
THAT'S ENOUGH.

06:51.645 --> 06:53.180
WHAT THE HELL IS THAT?

06:53.180 --> 06:56.884
THIS? IT'S KALE, BABY.
THIS IS NATURE'S SCRUB BRUSH.

06:56.884 --> 06:58.852
[ LAUGHS ] WHAT?
YOU AND JOAN STILL DOING
THAT CLEANSE?

06:58.852 --> 07:00.353
OF COURSE
I'M DOING THE CLEANSE.

07:00.353 --> 07:02.890
"THE CLEANSE"?
WHAT? ARE YOU WHIPPED?
YEAH.

07:02.890 --> 07:05.759
WHIPPED? DUDE, I AM
A HIGH-PERFORMANCE MACHINE.

07:05.759 --> 07:07.127
I NEED CLEAN FUEL
TO PUMP THESE PISTONS, BABY!

07:07.127 --> 07:08.762
[ Chuckling ]
"HIGH-PERFORMANCE MACHINE."

07:08.762 --> 07:10.564
HOW DO PASTRAMI SANDWICHES
FIT INTO ALL THAT?

07:10.564 --> 07:14.768
OH, YEAH.
HEY, WE SPEAK NOT ABOUT THE
PASTRAMI SANDWICHES, BRETHREN.

07:14.768 --> 07:16.637
DON'T YOU EVER
JUST DO SOMETHING...

07:16.637 --> 07:18.506
[ High-pitched voice ]
...BECAUSE YOUR WIFE
WANTS YOU TO DO IT?

07:18.506 --> 07:20.574
AW, HELL TO THE YEAH. I DON'T
TIE MY SHOES WITHOUT HER SAY-SO.

07:20.574 --> 07:23.511
WELL, THERE YOU GO.
John: GROWN MEN TERRIFIED.

07:23.511 --> 07:25.078
YOU DON'T HAVE THE RIGHT
TO HAVE AN OPINION

07:25.078 --> 07:27.047
TILL YOU'RE SPORTING
A BALL AND CHAIN, MY BROTHER.

07:27.047 --> 07:29.316
OH, YEAH? YOU KNOW WHAT?
MY CACTUS GARDEN IS JUST FINE.

07:29.316 --> 07:30.417
I GOT NO COMPLAINTS,
NO DEMANDS.

07:30.417 --> 07:31.852
"CACTUS GARDEN."

07:31.852 --> 07:33.186
[ Normal voice ]
DID YOU SAY "COCK-TUS" GARDEN?

07:33.186 --> 07:35.823
"CACTUS GARDEN."
IT'S QUITE PRICKLY!

07:35.823 --> 07:37.157
[ LAUGHTER ]
THAT SOUNDS REALLY GOOD.

07:37.157 --> 07:39.159
HOW ARE THEY IN BED?
THE "COCK-TUS."

07:39.159 --> 07:40.794
DISPATCHER:
Any available unit,

07:40.794 --> 07:44.131
we have a 415, female,
at 7812 South McCadden.

07:44.131 --> 07:46.500
OH.
HEY, HEY, HEY.
IT'S THEIR BOAT.

07:46.500 --> 07:48.401
JUST LET THE PROFESSIONALS
HANDLE THIS.

07:48.401 --> 07:49.436
[ INDISTINCT SHOUTING ]

07:49.436 --> 07:51.304
Sammy:
OH, GOD, HERE WE GO.

07:51.304 --> 07:54.474
YOU LOVE IT.
YOU'RE EATING IT UP.

07:54.474 --> 07:58.546
JUST DOING MY JOB, GUYS.
THAT'S ALL.

07:58.546 --> 08:01.414
HE LEARNED TO WRITE
IN PRISON,

08:01.414 --> 08:03.216
SO HE WROTE ME
AFTER A FEW YEARS

08:03.216 --> 08:06.286
AND TOLD ME
THAT I CHANGED HIS PATH

08:06.286 --> 08:07.621
AND WANTED
TO THANK ME.

08:07.621 --> 08:09.623
YOU DO NOT GET THAT
EVERY DAY.

08:09.623 --> 08:12.292
NO, YOU DON'T.
CORRESPONDED A BIT.

08:12.292 --> 08:16.029
I GUESS HE FEELS --
I DON'T KNOW -- CLOSE TO ME.

08:16.029 --> 08:17.665
WHAT DID HE DO?

08:17.665 --> 08:19.833
JUNKIE. STRUNG-OUT.

08:19.833 --> 08:24.204
BREAKING INTO PEOPLE'S HOMES
TO STEAL SMALL STUFF

08:24.204 --> 08:25.873
TO SUPPORT HIS HABIT.

08:25.873 --> 08:29.376
THIS WAS IN ARIZONA.
KILLED A COUPLE IN BED.

08:29.376 --> 08:32.746
THEN HE MOVED ON
TO NICE AND REMOTE CAMPSITES.

08:32.746 --> 08:35.082
[ BEEP ]
USUALLY TWO PEOPLE
BY THEMSELVES.

08:35.082 --> 08:37.885
THEN HE'D ROB THEM
FOR WHATEVER CASH THEY HAD.

08:37.885 --> 08:39.620
AND THEN
HE'D KILL THEM?

08:39.620 --> 08:42.623
YEAH. BEEN ON DEATH ROW
FOR LIKE 15 YEARS.

08:42.623 --> 08:45.525
[ POLICE RADIO CHATTER ]

08:50.998 --> 08:56.003
Jeanne: [ Sobbing ]
I DON'T KNOW WHAT TO DO.

08:56.003 --> 08:59.539
MA'AM?
OH, MY GOD.

08:59.539 --> 09:01.408
MA'AM, ARE YOU OKAY?

09:01.408 --> 09:03.744
ARE YOU GINA'S SON?

09:03.744 --> 09:05.613
NO, I'M A POLICE OFFICER,
MA'AM.

09:05.613 --> 09:06.947
ONE OF YOUR NEIGHBORS
SAID

09:06.947 --> 09:08.682
YOU'VE BEEN OUT HERE CRYING
ALL MORNING.

09:08.682 --> 09:11.685
IS THERE SOMEONE WE CAN CALL
TO HELP YOU OUT?

09:11.685 --> 09:13.353
UH...

09:13.353 --> 09:16.523
ARE YOU GINA'S SON?

09:16.523 --> 09:18.258
NO, MA'AM.

09:18.258 --> 09:21.428
OHH. OH.

09:21.428 --> 09:23.764
WHERE'S --
WHERE'S ARTHUR?

09:23.764 --> 09:25.265
Lucero:
WHO'S ARTHUR, MA'AM?

09:25.265 --> 09:29.803
HE'S MY HUSBAND!
I CAN'T FIND HIM ANYWHERE!

09:29.803 --> 09:32.305
[ Crying ] I LOOKED.
I DON'T KNOW WHERE HE --

09:32.305 --> 09:34.675
WHEN WAS THE LAST TIME
YOU SAW ARTHUR, MA'AM?

09:34.675 --> 09:38.211
[ SNIFFLES ]
UH...SAW HIM?

09:38.211 --> 09:40.547
UH...

09:40.547 --> 09:41.849
THIS MORNING.

09:41.849 --> 09:43.550
Lucero: COOP.

09:43.550 --> 09:46.720
I DON'T KNOW.
[ MUTTERING ]

09:46.720 --> 09:49.723
I GOT AN AUNT
WHO HAS ALZHEIMER'S, OKAY?

09:49.723 --> 09:51.024
SHE GOES THROUGH THIS
ALL THE TIME.

09:51.024 --> 09:52.726
SHE CAN'T FIND OUT
WHERE HER HUSBAND IS

09:52.726 --> 09:55.095
BECAUSE HE'S BEEN DEAD
FOR 30 YEARS.

09:55.095 --> 09:58.165
WE SHOULD CALL M.E.U.,
HAVE THEM TAKE CARE OF HER.

09:58.165 --> 10:01.969
[ SIGHING ]

10:01.969 --> 10:05.038
[ SNIFFLES, SIGHS ]

10:05.038 --> 10:06.039
MA'AM.

10:06.039 --> 10:08.175
[ SIGHS ]

10:08.175 --> 10:10.711
DO YOU HAVE A ROBE
OR SOMETHING UPSTAIRS?

10:10.711 --> 10:12.045
MM-HMM.

10:12.045 --> 10:14.414
OKAY. I'M GONNA GO GET
SOMETHING FOR YOU, OKAY?

10:14.414 --> 10:15.582
MM.
OKAY.

10:15.582 --> 10:17.284
THANK YOU.

10:45.112 --> 10:47.815
A57 -- REQUEST A SUPERVISOR
IN MY LOCATION.

10:47.815 --> 10:49.149
I GOT A D.B.

10:49.149 --> 10:52.720
ROLL OUT THE DETECTIVES...
AND M.E.U.

10:54.387 --> 10:56.857
SO...THE LAST TIME
THAT YOU SAW ARTHUR

10:56.857 --> 10:59.727
WAS THIS MORNING?

10:59.727 --> 11:02.062
HE WENT TO GET MILK.

11:02.062 --> 11:07.134
DO YOU HAVE ANY RECOLLECTION
OF AN INTRUDER IN THE HOUSE?

11:07.134 --> 11:09.937
WHO ARE YOU?

11:09.937 --> 11:11.939
I'M JOHN COOPER.

11:11.939 --> 11:14.942
I'M WITH THE LOS ANGELES
POLICE DEPARTMENT.

11:14.942 --> 11:18.278
WELL, IF YOU HAVE ANY QUESTIONS,
YOU CAN ASK ARTHUR.

11:18.278 --> 11:20.914
HE DEALS
WITH THOSE SORTS OF THINGS.

11:20.914 --> 11:23.616
YES, BUT DO YOU REMEMBER
A STRANGER IN THE HOUSE?

11:23.616 --> 11:27.154
MAYBE...AN ALTERCATION?

11:27.154 --> 11:28.621
AH.

11:28.621 --> 11:32.993
THERE WAS A MAN IN MY BATHROOM,
AND I HIT HIM WITH A HAMMER.

11:32.993 --> 11:34.494
YOU DON'T KNOW
WHO THE MAN WAS?

11:34.494 --> 11:37.564
I DON'T CARE.
THERE WAS A STRANGER IN MY HOME.

11:37.564 --> 11:39.166
SO I HIT HIM
WITH A HAMMER.

11:40.367 --> 11:42.235
IS IT WRONG
THAT WHILE WE'RE HERE

11:42.235 --> 11:46.239
UPDATING HOMICIDE BOOKS,
I'M PRAYING WE CATCH A CASE?

11:46.239 --> 11:48.108
Ruben: YES, IT IS.
[ SIGHS ]

11:48.108 --> 11:50.811
AND I'M DOING
THE EXACT SAME THING.

11:50.811 --> 11:53.814
HEY, LYDIA,
CHECK IT OUT.

11:53.814 --> 11:55.448
THAT WAS YOURS, RIGHT?

11:55.448 --> 11:57.384
YEAH. [ SIGHS ]
SOME OF US ARE MEETING
AT THE TEN RING

11:57.384 --> 11:58.886
TO CELEBRATE TONIGHT.

11:58.886 --> 12:02.255
YOU SHOULD COME DOWN.
BE OUR GUEST OF HONOR.

12:06.193 --> 12:09.729
ONE OF THE CAMPERS HE KILLED
WAS AN OFF-DUTY COP,

12:09.729 --> 12:12.432
WHICH ACCOUNTS
FOR ALL THE ENTHUSIASM

12:12.432 --> 12:14.234
FROM GENIUS OVER THERE.

12:14.234 --> 12:16.403
IT BOTHER YOU
HE'S CELEBRATING?

12:16.403 --> 12:18.939
OH, THEY DO
WHATEVER THEY WANT TO DO.

12:18.939 --> 12:21.641
JUST -- I DON'T KNOW.
IT DOESN'T SIT RIGHT WITH ME.

12:21.641 --> 12:25.312
YOU'RE NOT ENTHUSIASTIC
ABOUT GETTING A SERIAL KILLER?

12:25.312 --> 12:27.781
I DON'T THINK WE SHOULD BE
DANCING ON HIS GRAVE.

12:27.781 --> 12:30.083
SHOULDN'T BE HOLDING
HIS HAND, EITHER.

12:30.083 --> 12:32.585
I'M NOT. TRUST ME.

12:32.585 --> 12:35.288
I'M WORKING HIM, OKAY?
I THINK HE HAS BODIES ON HIM.

12:35.288 --> 12:38.325
A COUPLE CAMPERS THAT WENT
MISSING OUTSIDE OF PHOENIX.

12:38.325 --> 12:40.560
WHAT ARE THE COPS THERE SAYING?
THEY STOPPED LOOKING.

12:40.560 --> 12:43.931
CASE WENT COLD,
BUT...I THINK IT WAS HIM.

12:43.931 --> 12:45.632
AND AFTER TONIGHT,
WE'LL NEVER KNOW,

12:45.632 --> 12:46.967
SO I'VE BEEN GAINING
HIS TRUST

12:46.967 --> 12:48.902
WITH THE LETTERS
AND EVERYTHING,

12:48.902 --> 12:52.072
AND...BEST WAY
TO GET A CONFESSION IS TO...

12:52.072 --> 12:54.441
MAKE THEM THINK
THEY'RE YOUR BEST FRIEND, YEAH.

12:54.441 --> 12:55.708
DETECTIVES?
MM.

12:55.708 --> 12:59.746
I GOT A LADY HERE
THAT WANTS TO CONFESS A CRIME.

12:59.746 --> 13:02.916
WHEN DID YOU GET
YOUR GUARD CARD?

13:02.916 --> 13:05.252
A WHILE BACK.
I NEVER REALLY TAKE JOBS.

13:05.252 --> 13:07.120
BUT NOW WITH TAMMY
AND THE WHOLE CUSTODY BATTLE,

13:07.120 --> 13:08.822
ALL THE EXTRA EXPENSES --
LET ME ASK YOU SOMETHING.

13:08.822 --> 13:10.991
THEY ALWAYS SET YOU UP
GUARDING CELEBRITIES?

13:10.991 --> 13:13.994
NOT ALWAYS.
THOSE JOBS DO PAY THE BEST.

13:13.994 --> 13:16.796
IT'S A PRETTY GOOD GIG.
YEAH.

13:16.796 --> 13:20.200
TILL SOME WACKO DECIDES
TO SHOOT UP THE NEIGHBORHOOD.

13:20.200 --> 13:21.334
AW, COME ON.

13:21.334 --> 13:23.036
DON'T TELL ME
YOU DIDN'T LOVE EVERY MINUTE

13:23.036 --> 13:25.839
PLAYING BADASS
FOR THOSE CAMERAS.

13:25.839 --> 13:28.608
WHAT'S THE MATTER, SHERMAN?
AM I CROWDING YOUR SPOTLIGHT?

13:28.608 --> 13:29.943
HUH?

13:29.943 --> 13:31.945
PLEASE. PLEASE.

13:31.945 --> 13:34.747
HONESTLY, TAKE IT.
IT'S A RELIEF

13:34.747 --> 13:37.951
NOT HAVING ALL THAT...YOU KNOW,
THAT FOCUS, THAT WEIGHT.

13:37.951 --> 13:39.953
WHAT FOCUS?

13:39.953 --> 13:41.454
WHAT FOCUS?

13:41.454 --> 13:44.091
YOU KNOW, WITH THE, UH --
WITH THE POSTER AND EVERYTHING.

13:44.091 --> 13:46.960
OH, YEAH, YOU'RE REALLY LIVING
UNDER THE MICROSCOPE.

13:46.960 --> 13:49.963
[ LAUGHS ]
[ Chuckling ] SCREW YOU.

13:49.963 --> 13:53.000
HEY. HEY.
UP AHEAD. 2:00.

13:53.000 --> 13:56.536
HAND-TO-HAND.
LET'S HIT IT.
LET'S PLAY.

13:56.536 --> 13:58.038
WE LOST ONE.

13:58.038 --> 14:02.375
OKAY.
LET'S GO. LET'S GO.

14:02.375 --> 14:04.912
HEY, MAN.
TALK TO YOU FOR A MINUTE?

14:04.912 --> 14:06.779
HEY. HEY, NO!

14:06.779 --> 14:09.749
AW, SHIT.

14:09.749 --> 14:12.819
[ DOG BARKING IN DISTANCE ]

14:12.819 --> 14:14.487
[ TIRES SCREECH ]

14:14.487 --> 14:17.690
GET THE FUCK OUT OF THE WAY,
MAN!

14:17.690 --> 14:19.159
STAY DOWN, DIPSHIT!

14:19.159 --> 14:21.028
[ CAMERA SHUTTER CLICKING ]

14:21.028 --> 14:23.931
DID YOU FUCKING HEAR ME?
YOU BETTER --

14:26.066 --> 14:27.600
HEY, YOU MIND
TELLING YOUR FRIENDS

14:27.600 --> 14:28.969
TO STAY OUT OF OUR WAY?

14:28.969 --> 14:30.237
[ HANDCUFFS CLICK ]

14:30.237 --> 14:33.573
I WAS AT A PARK
AT 1st AND TOLUCA.

14:33.573 --> 14:37.444
AND I WAS...WAITING
OUTSIDE THE MEN'S ROOM,

14:37.444 --> 14:41.148
AND I SAW THIS SMALL MAN
GO INSIDE.

14:41.148 --> 14:43.483
AND HE WAS BALD.

14:43.483 --> 14:47.854
AND HE WAS STRONG
LIKE A JOCKEY.

14:47.854 --> 14:51.391
AND I FOLLOWED HIM INSIDE,
AND...

14:51.391 --> 14:53.193
[ SIGHS ]

14:53.193 --> 14:55.062
THIS IS VERY DIFFICULT.

14:55.062 --> 14:57.064
Lydia:
TAKE YOUR TIME.

14:57.064 --> 15:00.067
WELL...
[ SIGHS ]

15:00.067 --> 15:04.404
I RAPED HIM --
UP THE ASSHOLE.

15:04.404 --> 15:07.407
YOU RAPED -- RAPED HIM?
UH...

15:07.407 --> 15:10.978
OKAY, I'M -- I'M -- WHEN --
WHEN YOU SAY "RAPE,"

15:10.978 --> 15:14.514
WHAT EXACTLY DO --
OH. HERE.

15:14.514 --> 15:16.383
[ GRUNTS ]

15:16.383 --> 15:18.051
WITH THIS.

15:18.051 --> 15:20.387
OH. PERMISSION TO LEAVE.
THAT'S YOU, YO.

15:20.387 --> 15:22.589
AND YOUR DILDO --
THAT'S YOUR THING.

15:22.589 --> 15:24.124
[ SOBS ]

15:26.593 --> 15:28.095
I'M SORRY!

15:28.095 --> 15:29.963
WHAT THE FUCK, MOCO?

15:29.963 --> 15:31.298
WHAT THE HELL
DID YOU DO NOW, HUH?

15:31.298 --> 15:32.832
OKAY, WHOA, WHOA.
HEY! WHOA, WHOA.

15:32.832 --> 15:34.801
NO, NO,
HE'S MY BROTHER!

15:34.801 --> 15:36.769
WAS HE DEALING? HUH?
GOD, FUCK!

15:36.769 --> 15:38.838
I ASKED HIM TO COME FIX MY SINK,
AND HE DOES THIS SHIT!

15:38.838 --> 15:40.340
Ben: OKAY, ALL RIGHT.

15:40.340 --> 15:42.209
I GUESS I GOT ALL THE GOOD GENES
IN THIS FUCKING FAMILY

15:42.209 --> 15:43.910
'CAUSE HE'S
HALF-FUCKING-RETARDED!

15:43.910 --> 15:45.645
CALM DOWN. WE GOT TO TAKE HIM
TO THE STATION, OKAY?

15:45.645 --> 15:46.779
NAH! HE HAS MY KEYS.

15:46.779 --> 15:48.315
I GOT TO BE AT WORK
IN LIKE 20 MINUTES.

15:48.315 --> 15:50.183
[ SIGHS ] ALL RIGHT.
UH...HERE, LOOK.

15:50.183 --> 15:52.519
I CAN LET YOU IN,
BUT, UM...
OKAY.

15:52.519 --> 15:54.054
...THEY'RE GONNA HAVE TO GO BACK
ON HIM, OKAY?

15:54.054 --> 15:55.288
THEY'RE EVIDENCE NOW.
YEAH.

15:55.288 --> 15:57.157
ALL RIGHT?
SHOW ME WHERE YOU LIVE.

15:57.157 --> 16:00.327
HEY, I'M GONNA GO
CHECK THIS OUT.

16:00.327 --> 16:02.329
[ SIGHS ]
CRIS IS SUCH A FUCKING MORON.

16:02.329 --> 16:04.731
I TELL HIM THERE'S JUNKIES
IN FRONT OF MY BUILDING.

16:04.731 --> 16:07.934
AND INSTEAD OF SEEING THAT
AS A COMPLAINT,

16:07.934 --> 16:10.303
HE SEES THAT
AS A BUSINESS TIP.

16:13.006 --> 16:15.275
YEAH, WELL,
I CAN LEAVE MY BUSINESS CARD

16:15.275 --> 16:18.545
IN CASE YOU NEED US TO SCATTER
THE ADDICTS OR ANYTHING.

16:18.545 --> 16:20.047
YEAH, THANKS.

16:20.047 --> 16:23.216
SO, YOU, UH --
YOU PAINT, HUH?

16:23.216 --> 16:28.455
UH...YEAH, ACTUALLY.
WELL, I TAKE A CLASS AT L.A.S.C.

16:28.455 --> 16:32.659
OH.
I LIKE YOUR PLACE.

16:32.659 --> 16:33.826
THANK YOU.

16:33.826 --> 16:35.062
MM-HMM.

16:35.062 --> 16:36.929
WHAT'S YOUR GUESS
ON THE BODY?

16:36.929 --> 16:38.265
OH, THE WAY
IT WAS DECOMPOSED,

16:38.265 --> 16:40.133
I PUT THE OVER-UNDER
AT...NINE MONTHS.

16:40.133 --> 16:42.469
BUT I AM DEFINITELY TAKING
THE OVER.

16:42.469 --> 16:44.337
HOW DO YOU LIVE
WITH THAT SMELL?

16:44.337 --> 16:46.673
HOW ARE YOU DEAD FOR NINE MONTHS
AND NOBODY NOTICES?

16:46.673 --> 16:48.875
THEY WERE GETTING
ALL THEIR GROCERIES DELIVERED,

16:48.875 --> 16:50.210
PROBABLY HADN'T LEFT
IN YEARS.

16:50.210 --> 16:51.478
[ INDISTINCT SHOUTING ]

16:51.478 --> 16:53.046
DON'T YOU HAVE
FRIENDS, RELATIVES...

16:53.046 --> 16:55.415
I MEAN, PEOPLE WHO WOULD NOTICE
IF YOU WEREN'T AROUND?

16:55.415 --> 16:56.749
SOME PEOPLE ARE LIKE THAT,
I GUESS.

16:56.749 --> 17:02.955
KEEP TO THEMSELVES.
GOT NO KIDS, NO NOTHING.

17:02.955 --> 17:06.659
JUST A CACTUS GARDEN.

17:06.659 --> 17:08.995
[ LAUGHS ]

17:08.995 --> 17:10.197
ALL RIGHT.

17:10.197 --> 17:11.731
DON'T WORRY.
I'LL CHECK ON YOU, BROTHER.

17:11.731 --> 17:13.066
THANK YOU.

17:13.066 --> 17:14.567
[ LAUGHS ]

17:14.567 --> 17:17.104
DEWEY: A57,
in pursuit of a 211 suspect

17:17.104 --> 17:19.239
headed East
on 7th and Sutter.

17:19.239 --> 17:20.940
Requesting backup
and an airship.

17:20.940 --> 17:24.144
A57 -- SHOW US BACKING.

17:26.913 --> 17:30.250
AW, SHIT. THIS BITCH THINKS
HE CAN DRIVE, HUH?

17:30.250 --> 17:32.185
YOU GOT AN OPEN MIKE,
DEWEY.

17:32.185 --> 17:34.854
[ Laughs ]

17:34.854 --> 17:36.523
[ ENGINE REVS ]

17:36.523 --> 17:39.959
IT'S AN AUTOMATIC BEATDOWN
WHEN WE CATCH THIS BASTARD!

17:39.959 --> 17:41.761
Dewey,
you got an open mike.

17:41.761 --> 17:47.500
I'M ALL OVER THIS BITCH
LIKE A FAT KID ON A CUPCAKE.

17:53.106 --> 17:55.342
THIS BITCH IS GONNA NEED
AN R.A. UNIT.

17:55.342 --> 17:57.710
I AM BEATING HIS ASS!

17:59.612 --> 18:01.614
WE GOT HIM.
WE GOT HIM. WE GOT HIM.

18:01.614 --> 18:03.116
WE GOT HIM. WE GOT HIM.
GET READY TO CUT HIM OFF, OKAY?

18:03.116 --> 18:05.818
CUT HIM OFF.
CUT HIM OFF. CUT HIM OFF.

18:05.818 --> 18:08.555
HE'S JUMPING.

18:09.722 --> 18:11.224
STICK WITH THE BOOT.

18:11.224 --> 18:13.460
RIGHT. YOU, WITH ME.

18:16.429 --> 18:19.199
Dewey:
I AM ON YOUR ASS!

18:24.571 --> 18:27.940
John: DEWEY,
I'M RIGHT BEHIND YOU.

18:27.940 --> 18:29.809
DEWEY!

18:34.214 --> 18:36.549
A57 -- OFFICER DOWN!

18:36.549 --> 18:39.752
ROLL AN R.A. UNIT!
FRESNO STREET BRIDGE!

18:39.752 --> 18:42.922
DEWEY! DEWEY!

18:42.922 --> 18:46.226
HEY, MAN.

18:46.226 --> 18:48.728
OKAY, COME ON. COME ON.

18:48.728 --> 18:52.799
STICK WITH ME, BROTHER.
STAY WITH ME, BUDDY.

18:52.799 --> 18:53.966
[ BREATHING HEAVILY ]

18:53.966 --> 18:57.404
[ HORN BLARES ]

18:59.639 --> 19:01.408
[ CHUCKLES ] SHE MUST HAVE LEFT
HER TINFOIL HAT AT HOME.

19:01.408 --> 19:03.276
[ LAUGHS ]
OH, HERE WE GO.

19:03.276 --> 19:06.613
COLORADO HAS A BUNCH
OF BOGUS REPORTS BY HER.

19:06.613 --> 19:08.481
YOU GUYS GET A VISIT
FROM MELANIE?

19:08.481 --> 19:09.849
OH, YOU KNOW IT.
YEAH.

19:09.849 --> 19:10.750
[ CHUCKLES ] SURE.

19:10.750 --> 19:12.619
SHE TELL YOU
ABOUT CLINTON?

19:12.619 --> 19:14.987
[ SCOFFS ]
SHE IS A WINNER.

19:14.987 --> 19:16.323
CHICKEN DINNER.

19:16.323 --> 19:18.858
DO YOU HAVE ANYTHING REAL
FOR US?

19:18.858 --> 19:21.361
SORRY.

19:21.361 --> 19:24.764
WANT TO GET SOME LUNCH?
PHILIPPE'S?

19:24.764 --> 19:26.333
PHILIPPE'S?

19:26.333 --> 19:27.600
PHILIPPE'S.

19:27.600 --> 19:29.001
IT'S A SPANISH WORD.
PHILIPPE'S.

19:29.001 --> 19:31.204
IT IS NOT PHILIPPE'S.
IT IS NOT A SPANISH WORD.

19:31.204 --> 19:32.539
IT'S AN AMERICAN WORD?
PHILIPPE'S?

19:32.539 --> 19:35.074
IT STARTS WITH A P-H,
NOT AN "F."

19:35.074 --> 19:37.310
P-H -- IT'S PHILIPPE'S.

19:37.310 --> 19:39.479
Watters: HEY, CAPTAIN.

19:39.479 --> 19:43.182
BRYANT, LET ME SEE YOU
IN MY OFFICE.

19:43.182 --> 19:45.518
GO GET YOUR ATTABOY,
SUPERCOP.

19:53.960 --> 19:57.430
HAVE A SEAT.

19:59.198 --> 20:00.867
I HATE
TO TELL YOU THIS,

20:00.867 --> 20:02.735
BUT THIS THING
WITH YOUR WIFE,

20:02.735 --> 20:05.905
YOUR EX, WHATEVER,
IS NOT GONNA GO AWAY.

20:05.905 --> 20:08.641
THE INVESTIGATION'S BEING
TURNED OVER TO THE I.A.

20:08.641 --> 20:11.143
[ SIGHS ]

20:11.143 --> 20:12.745
WHAT ARE THEY SAYING?

20:12.745 --> 20:15.081
SAMMY, YOU KNOW
I CAN'T SAY ANYTHING.
[ SIGHS ]

20:15.081 --> 20:18.618
BUT SHE'S GOT MEDICAL RECORDS.
SHE WAS PRETTY BANGED UP.

20:18.618 --> 20:21.788
SHE WAS ATTACKING ME, OKAY?
I-I THREW HER OFF.

20:21.788 --> 20:25.325
EITHER WAY...
YOU SHOULD PROBABLY GET A REP.

20:25.325 --> 20:27.193
THEY'RE GONNA QUESTION YOU,
SAMMY.

20:27.193 --> 20:29.996
SHERMAN, TOO,
I'D IMAGINE.

20:29.996 --> 20:32.565
I JUST WANTED TO GIVE YOU
A HEADS UP.

20:35.167 --> 20:36.503
THANK YOU.

20:36.503 --> 20:39.105
YOU'RE WELCOME.

20:39.105 --> 20:42.609
I.A. UNBELIEVABLE.

20:42.609 --> 20:45.678
WHAT A USE FOR
DEPARTMENT RESOURCES THAT IS.

20:45.678 --> 20:48.615
BUNCH OF HALF-WITS
PLAYING AT BEING COPS.

20:48.615 --> 20:51.150
BEN, THIS IS SERIOUS.

20:51.150 --> 20:52.652
OH, COME ON.

20:52.652 --> 20:54.521
YOU REALLY THINK
THE DEPARTMENT'S GONNA MESS

20:54.521 --> 20:57.023
WITH THEIR
NEW GOLDEN BOY?

20:57.023 --> 20:59.592
THEY'RE PROBABLY GONNA
WANT TO TALK TO YOU, TOO.

20:59.592 --> 21:03.129
WELL, GOOD.
TRUST ME.

21:03.129 --> 21:04.797
I GOT YOUR BACK.

21:04.797 --> 21:07.900
[ SIGHS ]

21:07.900 --> 21:10.603
[ SIGHING ]

21:16.776 --> 21:18.911
HOW IS HE?

21:18.911 --> 21:23.115
HE, UH...
HE HAD A HEART ATTACK.

21:23.115 --> 21:24.451
[ SIGHS ]

21:24.451 --> 21:25.952
THEY'RE STILL WORKING
ON HIM.

21:25.952 --> 21:28.488
WON'T KNOW
FOR A FEW HOURS, BUT...

21:28.488 --> 21:31.491
HE DIDN'T LOOK GOOD.

21:31.491 --> 21:33.826
CAUGHT THE BASTARD.
AND?

21:33.826 --> 21:36.896
AND HE STOLE 40 BUCKS
AND A HANDFUL OF CANDY BARS

21:36.896 --> 21:38.230
FROM A NEWSSTAND.

21:38.230 --> 21:41.401
[ CHUCKLES ]

21:41.401 --> 21:43.636
YOU WANT TO
CALL IT A DAY?

21:43.636 --> 21:45.938
I CAN RIDE WITH SOMEONE ELSE
IF YOU WANT TO SLIDE OUT?

21:45.938 --> 21:49.776
LET'S GET BACK TO WORK.
[ SIGHS ]

21:53.212 --> 21:55.047
[ SIGHS ]

21:55.047 --> 21:58.618
[ POLICE RADIO CHATTER ]

21:58.618 --> 22:01.988
Chang: OH, MY GOSH.
LOOK WHO IT IS.

22:01.988 --> 22:04.457
HEY, BRYANT,
WILL YOU SIGN MY TITS?

22:04.457 --> 22:06.459
YOU'RE HILARIOUS, CHANG.
WHAT'S GOING ON?

22:06.459 --> 22:08.461
TWO-TREY GOT CRUSHED
BY A BLUE PICKUP.

22:08.461 --> 22:10.062
HIS GIRLFRIEND
SAW THE WHOLE THING.

22:10.062 --> 22:11.531
BUT YOGI'S KEEPING HER
ON A TIGHT LEASH,

22:11.531 --> 22:12.899
WON'T LET HER
TELL US MUCH.

22:12.899 --> 22:14.367
Ben: THINK HE HAD SOMETHING
TO DO WITH IT?

22:14.367 --> 22:16.536
PROBABLY WANTS TO
HANDLE IT HIMSELF.

22:16.536 --> 22:18.871
YEAH, IT'S ONE OF HIS BOYS
THAT GOT PANCAKED.

22:18.871 --> 22:21.574
ANYBODY TALKED
TO RICKY THE ROLLING TURD?

22:21.574 --> 22:23.743
[ CHUCKLES ]
BE MY GUEST.

22:23.743 --> 22:27.279
I'M GONNA STAY OVER HERE
AND NOT GET PINK EYE.

22:27.279 --> 22:29.348
HE'S MY HERO.

22:32.485 --> 22:33.986
[ CHUCKLES ]

22:33.986 --> 22:35.988
AMAZING TO THINK THAT FOR
EVERY ONE OF THESE PEOPLE

22:35.988 --> 22:38.891
THERE'S A PAIR
OF DISAPPOINTED PARENTS.

22:38.891 --> 22:41.894
[ CHUCKLES ]

22:41.894 --> 22:43.763
YOU ALL RIGHT?

22:46.533 --> 22:49.602
I'VE KNOWN DEWEY
A LONG TIME.

22:51.971 --> 22:53.973
HOW'D YOU GET THIS GUY --
FROM TONIGHT?

22:53.973 --> 22:56.676
NO, HE FLED TO L.A.
I WAS A P-1.

22:56.676 --> 22:58.678
AND I PICKED HIM UP
BUYING DOPE IN AN ALLEY.

22:58.678 --> 23:00.547
WON THE ASSHOLE
LOTTERY.

23:00.547 --> 23:02.214
HMM, YEAH,
BUT THAT FEELING --

23:02.214 --> 23:05.351
WHEN I FOUND OUT WHO I HAD AND
THAT HE WAS WANTED IN ARIZONA,

23:05.351 --> 23:06.853
WHAT HE WAS WANTED FOR...

23:06.853 --> 23:08.555
[ CHUCKLES ] THAT MOMENT,
THAT'S WHEN I KNEW

23:08.555 --> 23:10.723
I WANTED TO BE
A HOMICIDE DETECTIVE.

23:10.723 --> 23:12.224
MM-HMM.
BEEN CHASING IT EVER SINCE.

23:12.224 --> 23:15.127
EXCUSE ME. EXCUSE ME.
ARE YOU GUYS THE POLICE?

23:15.127 --> 23:16.429
YEAH.

23:16.429 --> 23:17.764
I DON'T KNOW
IF I'M IN THE RIGHT PLACE.

23:17.764 --> 23:19.499
BUT I FOUND THIS THING,

23:19.499 --> 23:22.034
AND I'M PRETTY SURE I SHOULD
HAND IT OVER TO YOU GUYS.
OKAY.

23:22.034 --> 23:23.870
I WAS GOING THROUGH MY
GRANDFATHER'S CRAP IN HIS ATTIC.

23:23.870 --> 23:25.738
HE ASKED ME
TO CLEAR IT OUT FOR HIM,

23:25.738 --> 23:27.440
SAID HE'D HELP PAY
FOR A NEW XBOX.

23:27.440 --> 23:28.941
MINE REALLY SUCKS.

23:28.941 --> 23:30.643
ANYWAY,
I FOUND THIS OLD, METAL BOX

23:30.643 --> 23:32.378
WITH ALL THIS WEIRD SHIT.
EXCUSE ME?

23:32.378 --> 23:35.247
SORRY.
"STUFF" IN IT.

23:35.247 --> 23:37.750
THANK YOU, SIR.

23:37.750 --> 23:40.487
HE FOUGHT IN VIETNAM.

23:42.421 --> 23:44.757
SON, STEP AWAY.
STEP AWAY FROM THAT.

23:44.757 --> 23:46.993
YOU GOT
LIVE EXPLOSIVES.

23:46.993 --> 23:50.697
LIVE EXPLOSIVES!
[ ALARM WAILING ]

23:50.697 --> 23:53.199
Keith: YOU BITCH!
I-I NEED MY MONEY!

23:53.199 --> 23:55.502
I GOT TO PAY MY FUCKING RENT!
CASH THAT DAMN CHECK!

23:55.502 --> 23:57.236
WHAT YOU MEAN
IT CAN'T BE VERIFIED?

23:57.236 --> 23:59.305
WHAT THE FUCK'S WRONG WITH YOU?
I WANT MY FUCKING CHECK CASHED!

23:59.305 --> 24:01.407
HEY!
LET'S STEP OUTSIDE, SIR.

24:01.407 --> 24:03.776
THIS BITCH TALK ABOUT SHE NOT
VERIFY MY FUCKING CHECK!
LET'S STEP OUTSIDE, SIR.

24:03.776 --> 24:04.944
WHAT THE HELL DOES THAT MEAN?
I NEED MY FUCKING MONEY!

24:04.944 --> 24:06.312
YOU CAN COME OUTSIDE NOW
OR IN --

24:06.312 --> 24:07.780
YOU CAN STEP OUTSIDE,
OR YOU CAN GET OUT OF HERE!

24:07.780 --> 24:09.782
I DON'T GIVE A FUCK.
LET GO OF ME!

24:09.782 --> 24:11.684
[ GRUNTS ]
HEY! HEY! COME ON!

24:11.684 --> 24:14.353
WHAT ARE YOU DOING?
STOP GRABBING ME! YOU
NEED TO GET THAT BITCH!

24:14.353 --> 24:15.988
AAH!

24:15.988 --> 24:18.324
[ GROANS ]

24:18.324 --> 24:20.459
TASER!

24:20.459 --> 24:21.894
TASER!

24:21.894 --> 24:23.229
AAH! OHH!

24:23.229 --> 24:25.231
[ GROANING, SCREAMING ]

24:28.935 --> 24:30.637
COOP!

24:32.572 --> 24:35.207
Sammy: YOU TALK TO HIM.
AND GOOD LUCK.

24:35.207 --> 24:37.009
THANKS FOR YOUR HELP.

24:37.009 --> 24:38.911
YO, I'M SURE
IT'S SOMEBODY IN 18th STREET.

24:38.911 --> 24:40.479
WE SHOULD PRESS THEM,
FIND OUT WHO.

24:40.479 --> 24:44.016
I TOLD THEM WHAT RICKY GAVE US.
IT'S UP TO THE DETECTIVES NOW.

24:44.016 --> 24:46.553
WE CAN DO IT OURSELVES.
[ CHUCKLES ]

24:46.553 --> 24:47.954
I GOT NO BURNING DESIRE

24:47.954 --> 24:49.989
TO FORCE MY WAY INTO
THE MIDDLE OF A GANG WAR TODAY.

24:49.989 --> 24:51.991
[ SCOFFS ]
WE CAN FIND THE GUY, THOUGH.

24:51.991 --> 24:53.793
Sammy: WE DID OUR JOB.
LET THEM DO THEIRS.

24:53.793 --> 24:55.795
IF THEY NEED OUR HELP,
THEY KNOW WHERE TO FIND US.

24:55.795 --> 24:57.797
I DON'T KNOW WHY
WE CAN'T SEE A THING THROUGH.

24:57.797 --> 25:00.733
TAKE THE DETECTIVE EXAM
IF YOU WANT.
I WILL.

25:00.733 --> 25:03.903
AND TELL YOU WHAT -- WHEN I DO,
I'M NOT GONNA VOLUNTEER

25:03.903 --> 25:05.905
TO COME BACK DOWN
AND DEAL WITH THIS CRAP.

25:05.905 --> 25:08.074
I HAD THIS CASE ONCE,

25:08.074 --> 25:10.242
80-YEAR-OLD LADY
EXECUTED IN HER LIVING ROOM,

25:10.242 --> 25:12.111
NO POSSIBLE MOTIVE,
NOTHING STOLEN,

25:12.111 --> 25:13.813
NOT A FINGERPRINT
IN THE WHOLE PLACE.

25:13.813 --> 25:15.982
JUST A SINGLE BULLET
TO THE BRAIN.

25:15.982 --> 25:17.850
FOR 18 MONTHS,
I WENT TO SLEEP,

25:17.850 --> 25:20.920
WOKE UP
THINKING ABOUT THAT LADY.

25:23.355 --> 25:28.561
NICE THING ABOUT PATROL,
WHEN THE DAY'S OVER, IT'S OVER.

25:28.561 --> 25:30.763
CLEAN SLATE EVERY DAY.

25:38.738 --> 25:42.742
OFFICER COOPER,
WE LOOKED AT YOUR MRI.

25:42.742 --> 25:44.744
THERE IS A HERNIATION
IN ONE OF YOUR DISCS,

25:44.744 --> 25:46.078
BUT IT IS VERY MINOR.

25:46.078 --> 25:47.814
IT SHOULD HEAL ON ITS OWN
IN A COUPLE OF WEEKS.

25:47.814 --> 25:49.281
HURT LIKE HELL.

25:49.281 --> 25:52.284
I'M SURE IT DID, BUT THAT
WAS PROBABLY JUST THE IMPACT.

25:52.284 --> 25:54.153
NEVER FEELS GOOD
TO LAND LIKE THAT.

25:54.153 --> 25:55.822
YOU ALSO MIGHT HAVE
TENSED UP

25:55.822 --> 25:57.590
WHEN YOU FELT
THAT FAMILIAR PAIN.

25:57.590 --> 25:58.925
I SEE IT ALL THE TIME

25:58.925 --> 26:00.326
WITH PEOPLE WHO'VE HAD
BACK INJURIES IN THE PAST.

26:00.326 --> 26:03.195
WILL I MISS WORK? [ SIGHS ]
I WOULDN'T THINK SO.

26:03.195 --> 26:05.064
WE'LL GIVE YOU
SOME HIGH-DOSE IBUPROFEN.
[ SIGHS ]

26:05.064 --> 26:07.233
OR, IF THE PAIN'S REALLY BAD,
I COULD GIVE YOU SOME VICODIN.

26:07.233 --> 26:10.102
NO, THE IBUPROFEN
WILL BE JUST FINE.

26:10.102 --> 26:12.138
WE'LL HAVE YOU OUT OF HERE
IN A FEW MINUTES.

26:12.138 --> 26:14.641
[ SIGHS ] THANKS.

26:14.641 --> 26:17.644
Laurie: EXCUSE ME.
I'M...A FRIEND.

26:17.644 --> 26:19.311
HEY.
HEY.

26:19.311 --> 26:23.515
I...PEEKED AT YOUR CHARTS.
EVERYTHING SEEMS TO CHECK OUT.

26:23.515 --> 26:25.317
HOW ARE YOU?

26:25.317 --> 26:28.821
GOOD. I'VE BEEN GOOD.

26:28.821 --> 26:30.690
I'M SORRY
I'VE BEEN OUT OF TOUCH LATELY.

26:30.690 --> 26:32.391
YEAH,
WE'RE BOTH GUILTY THERE.

26:32.391 --> 26:33.960
MM.
[ INHALES SHARPLY ]

26:33.960 --> 26:36.295
WELL, WE'LL HAVE TO
GET BETTER AT THAT.
OKAY.

26:36.295 --> 26:39.832
DID THEY, UM -- THEY GIVE YOU
SOMETHING FOR THE PAIN?

26:39.832 --> 26:43.836
IBUPROFEN.
[ SIGHS ] GREAT.

26:43.836 --> 26:46.338
LOOK, I...
CAN'T STOP WORRYING ABOUT YOU

26:46.338 --> 26:49.608
JUST 'CAUSE
WE'RE NOT MARRIED ANYMORE.

26:52.779 --> 26:56.883
IT'S GOOD TO SEE YOU,
JOHN.

26:59.618 --> 27:02.121
[ SIRENS WAILING ]

27:02.121 --> 27:05.191
[ SCOFFS ]
WHAT A CIRCUS.

27:06.893 --> 27:09.762
THIS IS GONNA SOUND KIND OF --
KIND OF CRAZY,

27:09.762 --> 27:13.766
BUT, UH...
ARE YOU GONNA WATCH TONIGHT?

27:13.766 --> 27:17.636
NO. I-I MEAN,
IF HE WANTS ME IN THE ROOM,

27:17.636 --> 27:21.640
I'LL BE THERE,
BUT I'M NOT GONNA WATCH.

27:21.640 --> 27:25.511
WHAT'S YOUR TAKE
ON THE DEATH PENALTY?

27:25.511 --> 27:28.915
I'M FOR IT. YOU?
[ SCOFFS ]

27:28.915 --> 27:31.017
FOR DAMN SURE,
I AIN'T FOR THIS BROKE-ASS STATE

27:31.017 --> 27:32.919
PAYING FOR A BUNCH OF FOOLS
ON DEATH ROW

27:32.919 --> 27:36.923
TO FILE FOR APPEALS, BUT,
YEAH, I'M FOR IT, IF WE USE IT.

27:36.923 --> 27:39.091
I FEEL LIKE
IF YOU CROSS A CERTAIN LINE,

27:39.091 --> 27:41.961
YOU SHOULD PAY
THE ULTIMATE PRICE.

27:41.961 --> 27:43.830
YEAH, BUT IT'S...
A LITTLE DIFFERENT

27:43.830 --> 27:46.165
WHEN IT'S YOUR PEN PAL
GETTING THE NEEDLE.

27:46.165 --> 27:48.868
HE'S NOT MY PEN PAL.
NAH, I KNOW.

27:48.868 --> 27:50.870
I DIDN'T MEAN ANYTHING.
IT'S JUST...

27:50.870 --> 27:52.138
[ SIGHS ]

27:52.138 --> 27:54.673
LOOK, I KNOW
IT'S GOT TO BE VERY COMPLICATED.

27:54.673 --> 27:58.677
NOT REALLY.
I MEAN, GUY'S A MONSTER.

27:58.677 --> 28:00.512
NOW HE'S GONNA
REAP THE WHIRLWIND.

28:00.512 --> 28:03.649
THERE IT IS.
"GOOD RIDDANCE."

28:03.649 --> 28:06.518
PRETTY MUCH.

28:06.518 --> 28:09.055
[ SIGHS ]

28:13.893 --> 28:16.963
YOU GOT A PLANE TO CATCH,
PARTNER.

28:20.232 --> 28:24.103
FOR REAL? YOU THINK
I'D BE A GOOD DETECTIVE?

28:24.103 --> 28:25.271
I DON'T KNOW, SHERMAN.

28:25.271 --> 28:27.139
I MEAN,
I WAS A GREAT DETECTIVE,

28:27.139 --> 28:29.675
BUT YOU DON'T REALLY HAVE
MY SMARTS, YOU KNOW?

28:29.675 --> 28:31.343
OR MY LOOKS,
FOR THAT MATTER.

28:31.343 --> 28:34.413
YEAH. BUT YOU KNOW WHAT?
THANK GOD FOR THAT.

28:40.586 --> 28:43.756
Lucero:
COOPER, YOU ALL RIGHT?

28:43.756 --> 28:45.024
[ SIGHS ] YEAH.

28:45.024 --> 28:46.926
I'LL BE BACK TO NORMAL
IN A FEW DAYS.

28:46.926 --> 28:49.929
IT WAS A FALSE ALARM.
OH, THANK JESUS.

28:49.929 --> 28:51.263
[ SMOOCHES, SIGHS ]

28:51.263 --> 28:52.799
I THOUGHT
I SCREWED YOU UP FOR LIFE.

28:52.799 --> 28:54.801
NO, I'M FINE.

28:54.801 --> 28:56.803
NEXT TIME...
[ SIGHS ]

28:56.803 --> 28:58.838
...JUST GO AHEAD
AND SHOOT THE GUY, THOUGH.

28:58.838 --> 29:01.173
ROGER THAT. I DON'T KNOW
WHAT I WAS THINKING.

29:01.173 --> 29:03.175
I WAS JUST TRYING
TO TACKLE A MAN AND ENDED UP

29:03.175 --> 29:05.644
DROPPING 300 POUNDS ON
YOUR SURGICALLY REPAIRED SPINE.

29:05.644 --> 29:07.914
THE DOC SAID
THE SURGERY LOOKED GOOD.

29:07.914 --> 29:09.782
GOOD. THAT'S GOOD.

29:09.782 --> 29:12.084
YOU NEED HELP?
NO.

29:12.084 --> 29:13.953
HOW'D YOU MESS IT UP
IN THE FIRST PLACE?

29:13.953 --> 29:17.489
[ SIGHS ] I DON'T KNOW.

29:17.489 --> 29:20.459
I'M NOT SURE.

29:20.459 --> 29:24.463
THERE WAS A WRECK...
10, 12 YEARS AGO.

29:24.463 --> 29:26.999
DURING A PURSUIT, THIS COP,
BRAND-NEW, HIS CAR FLIPPED.

29:26.999 --> 29:28.534
HE WAS TRAPPED INSIDE.
[ SIGHS ]

29:28.534 --> 29:30.036
THE TIME I GOT THERE,

29:30.036 --> 29:32.738
THE...CAR HAD ALREADY
STARTED BURNING.

29:32.738 --> 29:34.240
HE WAS SCREAMING.

29:34.240 --> 29:39.111
TRIED TO PRY THE DOOR OPEN.
I JUST FELT SOMETHING.

29:39.111 --> 29:41.047
THEN,
IT WAS JUST A PINCH,

29:41.047 --> 29:42.514
BUT MAYBE
THAT'S WHEN IT STARTED.

29:42.514 --> 29:44.984
I DON'T KNOW. I WAS GOOD
FOR YEARS AFTER THAT, BUT...

29:44.984 --> 29:48.154
DOC SAYS
IT WAS JUST WEAR AND TEAR.

29:48.154 --> 29:51.157
SO, WHAT THE HELL,
MAN?

29:51.157 --> 29:55.694
AND...DID HE MAKE IT?
DID YOU GET THE DOOR OPEN?

29:55.694 --> 29:59.531
YEAH. HE MADE IT.

29:59.531 --> 30:04.070
[ LAUGHS ] THERE HE IS.
PUT HER THERE. MY MAN.

30:04.070 --> 30:05.737
YOU KNOW,
WE DID A ROUTINE TRAFFIC STOP

30:05.737 --> 30:07.273
ON WHAT'S-HIS-NAME
EARLIER TODAY.
YEAH?

30:07.273 --> 30:09.141
THIS GUY'S TRUNK
WAS A GOLD MINE.

30:09.141 --> 30:11.343
I'M TALKING WEED, PILLS,
COKE, "E," YOU NAME IT.

30:11.343 --> 30:12.945
WE DID A ROLLBACK
TO HIS PAD.

30:12.945 --> 30:14.346
WE GOT THE MOTHER LODE, BABY.
YOU GOT TO SEE IT.

30:14.346 --> 30:15.647
NOT BAD.
NOT BAD?

30:15.647 --> 30:17.649
THAT'S BEAUTIFUL
IS WHAT THAT IS.
[ LAUGHS ]

30:17.649 --> 30:20.452
LOOK, WE'RE BUYING YOUR DRINKS
TONIGHT AT THE TEN RING. YOU IN?

30:20.452 --> 30:22.154
YEAH. YEAH,
JUST GIVE ME A FEW MINUTES

30:22.154 --> 30:23.355
TO WRAP UP HERE,
ALL RIGHT?

30:23.355 --> 30:24.756
ALL RIGHT.
ALL RIGHT, MAN.

30:24.756 --> 30:25.958
BEN SHERMAN.
[ LAUGHS ]

30:25.958 --> 30:27.293
MAN.
YOU...MADE MY DAY.

30:27.293 --> 30:30.829
MY PLEASURE.
I'LL SEE YOU.

30:30.829 --> 30:32.831
[ SNIFFS ]

30:32.831 --> 30:34.166
[ SIGHS ]

30:34.166 --> 30:37.169
SO,
YOU WANT TO COME WITH?

30:37.169 --> 30:38.704
NAH,
I-I GOT NATE TONIGHT, MAN.

30:38.704 --> 30:41.240
AW, COME ON, MAN.

30:41.240 --> 30:44.443
YOU HAD YOUR HERO MOMENT.
I GOT THIS THING.

30:44.443 --> 30:45.711
WE SHOULD CELEBRATE.

30:45.711 --> 30:48.014
NOT TONIGHT.

30:48.014 --> 30:51.383
YEAH. [ SNIFFS ]

30:51.383 --> 30:53.052
WHEW!

30:53.052 --> 30:56.422
[ LOCK CLICKS ]
HAVE FUN CHANGING DIAPERS.

30:56.422 --> 30:58.324
ALWAYS DO.

30:58.324 --> 31:00.492
Dewey: YOU'RE ALMOST
THE MAN OF THE HOUSE, RAE-RAE.

31:00.492 --> 31:02.194
Rae Ann: IT'S LOOKING LIKE
I AM THE MAN OF THE HOUSE.

31:02.194 --> 31:05.364
[ LAUGHTER ]
OHH.
THAT'S NOT FUNNY THERE.

31:05.364 --> 31:09.701
OH, OH, LORD. OH, GOD.
HERE HE IS, LADIES.

31:09.701 --> 31:12.838
THE MAN OF THE HOUR,
OFFICER JONATHAN COOPER,

31:12.838 --> 31:14.840
THE BEST KISSER
I'VE EVER KISSED.

31:14.840 --> 31:17.343
I GUESS YOU'RE OKAY THEN.
YEAH, BUDDY.

31:17.343 --> 31:20.079
I'M READY
TO HIT THE STREETS RIGHT NOW.

31:20.079 --> 31:22.414
HOW YOU GUYS HOLDING UP?

31:22.414 --> 31:25.584
WE'RE USED TO
HIM BEING INCAPACITATED, SO...

31:25.584 --> 31:27.954
HEY, WHEN YOU'RE DONE
FONDLING MY DAUGHTER,

31:27.954 --> 31:29.121
COME OVER HERE,
SIT DOWN.

31:29.121 --> 31:31.157
[ LAUGHTER ]

31:31.157 --> 31:34.526
[ GRUNTS ]
I GOT TO ASK YOU SOMETHING.

31:34.526 --> 31:37.329
[ BREATHING DEEPLY ]

31:37.329 --> 31:40.032
HOW MANY
DO I OWE YOU NOW, MAN?

31:40.032 --> 31:41.533
[ SIGHS ]

31:41.533 --> 31:44.836
YOU DON'T OWE ME SHIT.
NO, I DO.

31:44.836 --> 31:47.539
YOU SAVED MY ASS
SO MANY TIMES.

31:47.539 --> 31:50.042
HEY, LET ME ASK YOU...

31:50.042 --> 31:54.213
WHEN YOU WERE GIVING ME
MOUTH-TO-MOUTH...

31:54.213 --> 31:57.549
DID YOU SLIP A LITTLE TONGUE
IN THERE?

31:57.549 --> 31:59.952
HUH? 'CAUSE WHEN I WOKE UP
IN HERE, MAN,

31:59.952 --> 32:01.753
I WAS HARD AS A ROCK.
[ CHUCKLES ]

32:01.753 --> 32:03.822
BUT ALL I COULD THINK ABOUT
WAS YOU.
OKAY.

32:03.822 --> 32:05.491
[ LAUGHS ]
ALL RIGHT, DEWEY.

32:05.491 --> 32:08.027
VIAGRA'S GOT NOTHING
ON THIS GUY RIGHT HERE.

32:08.027 --> 32:10.529
Rae Ann: DAD.
[ LAUGHTER ]

32:10.529 --> 32:13.065
TAKE CARE OF YOURSELF,
OFFICER DUDEK.

32:13.065 --> 32:15.401
HEY, I LOVE YOU, MAN.
I DO.

32:15.401 --> 32:17.936
I'M IN LOVE WITH YOU.

32:17.936 --> 32:20.272
GOD,
LOOK AT THAT BUTT.

32:20.272 --> 32:23.542
OH, HE'S SO CUTE.
[ LAUGHS ]

32:25.277 --> 32:27.479
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS ]

32:39.591 --> 32:41.293
HEY.
HEY.

32:43.195 --> 32:46.698
HEARD ABOUT DEWEY.
HOW IS HE?

32:46.698 --> 32:50.236
I WENT AND SAW HIM.
HE'S, UH, GONNA BE FINE.

32:50.236 --> 32:53.739
THANK GOD. CRAZY.

32:53.739 --> 32:56.108
YOU CELEBRATING
YOUR BIG NARC BUST?

32:56.108 --> 32:59.811
[ CHUCKLES ]
HEARD ABOUT THAT?

32:59.811 --> 33:03.515
GUYS WERE TALKING.

33:03.515 --> 33:04.850
HMM.

33:04.850 --> 33:07.986
HOW'D YOU
FIGURE THAT ONE OUT?

33:07.986 --> 33:12.724
UH, YOU KNOW, JUST USING
MY OB SKILLS LIKE YOU TAUGHT ME.

33:12.724 --> 33:15.227
[ BOTH LAUGH ]

33:15.227 --> 33:18.730
YEAH, WELL,
YOU KNOW HOW IT IS.

33:18.730 --> 33:22.468
DOESN'T MATTER WHERE YOU ARE.
ALWAYS ON PATROL.

33:22.468 --> 33:25.171
DON'T YOU GOT BETTER THINGS
YOU CAN BE DOING WITH YOUR TIME?

33:25.171 --> 33:28.674
"GREATEST SHOW ON EARTH,"
YOU ALWAYS TOLD ME.

33:28.674 --> 33:31.043
TRYING TO GIVE YOU
SOME ADVICE HERE, NUMB NUTS.

33:31.043 --> 33:32.744
AND WHAT'S THAT?

33:35.181 --> 33:38.184
FORGET IT.

33:38.184 --> 33:41.353
[ PILLS RATTLE ]

33:41.353 --> 33:45.357
[ SNIFFS ]
WELL. DON'T WORRY.

33:45.357 --> 33:47.859
NOT GONNA PISS AWAY MY LIFE
ON PATROL FOR 20 YEARS.

33:47.859 --> 33:50.062
I'M THINKING ABOUT
TAKING THE DETECTIVE EXAM.

33:50.062 --> 33:54.066
[ CHUCKLES ]
GOD HELP US ALL.

33:54.066 --> 33:58.937
DRINKING AGAIN?
I NEVER REALLY STOPPED.

33:58.937 --> 34:00.806
[ PILLS RATTLE ]

34:04.243 --> 34:06.778
ALL RIGHT.
[ SIGHS ]

34:24.096 --> 34:27.466
HEY, VICTOR. IT'S SAMMY.

34:27.466 --> 34:28.967
HEY.

34:28.967 --> 34:32.138
YEAH, D--
NO. DON'T HANG UP.

34:32.138 --> 34:35.241
JUST -- JUST LISTEN TO ME
FOR ONE SECOND.

34:35.241 --> 34:39.778
VICTOR, CALM DOWN.

34:39.778 --> 34:43.115
OKAY? OKAY.

34:43.115 --> 34:47.119
I JUST...

34:47.119 --> 34:49.121
DO YOU THINK
THERE'S ANY POSSIBLE WAY

34:49.121 --> 34:51.323
THAT I COULD TALK TO TAMMY?

34:53.759 --> 34:56.828
OKAY, OKAY.
OKAY, YES, I GET IT.

34:56.828 --> 34:58.630
I JUST...
[ SIGHS ]

34:58.630 --> 35:00.499
[ Voice breaking ]
I HAD A TOUGH DAY TODAY, VICTOR,

35:00.499 --> 35:04.370
AND I...JUST REALLY WANTED
TO TELL HER THAT I'M SORRY.

35:04.370 --> 35:05.737
COULD YOU TELL HER THAT FOR ME?

35:05.737 --> 35:08.907
THAT I'M SORRY
FOR HOW ALL THIS HAS...BEEN?

35:08.907 --> 35:12.811
PLEASE, VICTOR,
COULD YOU JUST TELL HER THAT?

35:12.811 --> 35:14.513
[ Click ]

35:14.513 --> 35:16.382
HELLO?

35:19.985 --> 35:21.853
HELLO?

35:26.958 --> 35:31.630
LYDIA. [ SIGHS ]
OH, MAN.

35:31.630 --> 35:34.333
I WAS ALL AFRAID
YOU WEREN'T GONNA MAKE IT.

35:34.333 --> 35:37.436
HERE I AM.
HERE YOU ARE.

35:37.436 --> 35:42.774
GOT ANY GOOD COP STORIES
FOR ME?

35:42.774 --> 35:45.477
OHH. JUST TODAY,
THERE WERE A BUNCH.

35:45.477 --> 35:47.646
UM...
THIS CRAZY LADY CAME IN,

35:47.646 --> 35:50.982
AND SHE LIKES TO
CONFESS TO MADE-UP CRIMES.

35:50.982 --> 35:54.986
UM...SHE SAID
SHE RAPED A MAN IN A BATHROOM.

35:54.986 --> 35:56.588
SHE ALSO SAID

35:56.588 --> 35:59.491
SHE'S HAVING A TELEPATHIC
LOVE AFFAIR WITH BILL CLINTON.

35:59.491 --> 36:01.193
[ Chuckling ] WILD!

36:01.193 --> 36:04.196
WELL, UH, I WOULDN'T
PUT IT PAST SLICK WILLIE.

36:04.196 --> 36:07.199
[ CHUCKLES ]

36:07.199 --> 36:09.535
HAD YOUR DINNER YET?

36:09.535 --> 36:13.239
UH, FRIED OKRA
AND BANANA BREAD.

36:13.239 --> 36:14.906
SOUNDS GOOD.

36:14.906 --> 36:19.245
UH...COULDN'T KEEP IT DOWN.
TOO DAMN NERVOUS.

36:21.480 --> 36:24.015
ANYTHING YOU WANT TO
TELL ME, ERIC?

36:24.015 --> 36:25.884
BEFORE...

36:25.884 --> 36:29.388
YEAH. OHH.

36:29.388 --> 36:34.260
YEAH, I'M --
I'M GLAD YOU ASKED.

36:34.260 --> 36:36.428
'CAUSE...

36:36.428 --> 36:40.966
I WAS IN A REAL BAD WAY
BEFORE YOU CAUGHT ME, YOU KNOW?

36:40.966 --> 36:42.468
I...
[ SIGHS ]

36:42.468 --> 36:45.804
MY WHOLE LIFE WAS JUST UGLY,
YOU KNOW?

36:45.804 --> 36:49.341
LIKE, MY CHILDHOOD,
AND I SAW THINGS A KID...

36:49.341 --> 36:51.209
SHOULDN'T SEE, YOU KNOW?

36:51.209 --> 36:53.279
[ SIGHS ]

36:55.080 --> 37:00.819
YOU WERE THE FIRST REAL LIGHT.
YOU KNOW WHAT I MEAN?

37:00.819 --> 37:02.788
YEAH.

37:02.788 --> 37:06.958
I-I REMEMBER...
W-WHEN YOU CAUGHT ME THAT,

37:06.958 --> 37:10.329
LIKE, IN MY HEAD,
I WAS LIKE, "THANK YOU.

37:10.329 --> 37:11.663
THANK YOU. THANK YOU."

37:11.663 --> 37:14.833
LIKE...I WAS WAITING
FOR YOU TO COME ALONG

37:14.833 --> 37:17.068
AND TAKE ME
OUT OF THE WORLD.

37:17.068 --> 37:19.571
YEAH.

37:19.571 --> 37:21.773
AND SAY WHAT YOU WILL
ABOUT THIS PLACE.

37:21.773 --> 37:26.312
IT WAS GOOD FOR ME.
YOU KNOW?

37:26.312 --> 37:29.114
I MEAN,
IT'S SCARY, BUT...

37:29.114 --> 37:32.451
NOTHING'S AS SCARY
AS WHAT'S GOING ON UP HERE.

37:32.451 --> 37:36.788
GLAD YOU FOUND
SOME KIND OF PEACE.

37:36.788 --> 37:40.125
IS THERE ANYTHING ELSE
YOU WANT TO GET OFF YOUR CHEST?

37:40.125 --> 37:43.495
ANY WEIGHT YOU NEED LIFTED?
WAIT, WAIT, WAIT.

37:43.495 --> 37:45.497
WHAT KIND OF WEIGHT?
WHAT ARE YOU TALKING ABOUT?

37:45.497 --> 37:48.367
I DON'T KNOW.
ANYTHING UNRESOLVED?

37:48.367 --> 37:50.836
AW, SHIT. [ LAUGHS ]

37:50.836 --> 37:53.705
YOU'RE WORKING ME
RIGHT NOW, HUH?

37:53.705 --> 37:56.375
I'M JUST ASKING.
NO, JUST SPIT IT OUT.

37:56.375 --> 38:00.446
THAT COUPLE THAT WENT MISSING
AT ROCK POINT CAMPGROUNDS...

38:00.446 --> 38:04.616
1995, NEVER FOUND.

38:04.616 --> 38:08.153
MATCHED YOUR M.O.

38:08.153 --> 38:10.356
I ASKED YOU HERE
AS A FRIEND.

38:10.356 --> 38:12.791
I'VE BEEN A FRIEND.
I ANSWERED YOUR LETTERS.

38:12.791 --> 38:15.494
I CHOSE TO SPEND THIS TIME
WITH YOU.

38:15.494 --> 38:17.028
THOSE FAMILIES
DESERVE CLOS--

38:17.028 --> 38:20.532
NO! NO, NO!

38:20.532 --> 38:22.734
NO.
DON'T PUT IT OFF ON THEM.

38:22.734 --> 38:24.670
THIS ISN'T ABOUT THOSE FAMILIES.
IT'S ABOUT YOU.

38:24.670 --> 38:26.538
TELL ME WHERE
THE BODIES ARE, ERIC.

38:26.538 --> 38:30.241
THIS SURPRISES ME,
LYDIA.

38:30.241 --> 38:32.310
REALLY.

38:34.012 --> 38:39.084
WELL, IT WAS NICE OF YOU
TO WRITE THOSE LETTERS.

38:39.084 --> 38:41.086
YOU'RE A GOOD PERSON.

38:41.086 --> 38:44.890
FOR ME...

38:44.890 --> 38:49.728
I GOT A LOT OUT OF WRITING THEM
AND RECEIVING YOURS.

38:49.728 --> 38:53.365
ADMIT THAT YOU DID,
TOO.

38:55.767 --> 38:57.769
YOU HAVE A CHANCE
TO DO SOMETHING GOOD HERE.

38:57.769 --> 39:00.939
A PERSON WOULDN'T
MAKE THOSE KIND OF THINGS UP.

39:00.939 --> 39:04.476
YOUR SON
WON'T STOP CRYING.

39:04.476 --> 39:06.778
YOU WONDER IF YOU
WEREN'T SUPPOSED TO BE A MOM.

39:06.778 --> 39:09.981
YOU -- YOU THINK MAYBE YOU'RE
SUPPOSED TO FEEL SOMETHING

39:09.981 --> 39:11.850
THAT YOU'RE NOT.

39:14.820 --> 39:17.423
I DON'T KNOW
IF YOU TOLD ME THOSE THINGS

39:17.423 --> 39:20.025
BECAUSE YOU DIDN'T HAVE
ANYBODY ELSE TO TELL,

39:20.025 --> 39:26.197
BUT, SHIT...I KNOW THOSE LETTERS
WERE ABOUT MORE THAN JUST ME.

39:26.197 --> 39:28.734
LYDIA.

39:30.436 --> 39:33.439
WHATEVER YOU SAY, ERIC.

39:33.439 --> 39:35.707
NOW,
DID YOU KILL THOSE PEOPLE?

39:37.443 --> 39:40.512
BE REAL WITH ME.

39:43.782 --> 39:49.855
TELL ME HIS NAME -- YOUR SON.
YOU NEVER TOLD ME HIS NAME.

40:01.800 --> 40:05.471
Christopher.

40:05.471 --> 40:07.839
[ CELLPHONE RINGING ]

40:12.010 --> 40:17.348
HELLO.

40:17.348 --> 40:19.718
HEY.

40:40.238 --> 40:42.440
[ SIRENS WAILING IN DISTANCE ]

40:47.813 --> 40:51.550
[ DOG BARKING IN DISTANCE ]
